        <mxCell id="sec_out_d" parent="1" style="text;html=0;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=9;fontColor=#cc8899;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=2;" value="mask_secrets() — scan for 16 secret patterns in response&#xa;  API keys (Anthropic, OpenAI, DeepSeek, Groq, HF, GitHub, AWS...)&#xa;  JWTs, private keys, bearer tokens, passwords&#xa;  ALL matches replaced with ***REDACTED***&#xa;&#xa;detect_pii() — scan for 8 PII types in response&#xa;  email, phone, SSN, credit card, IPv4, passport, IBAN&#xa;  Action: redact_and_warn or block per config&#xa;&#xa;check_content() — verify response doesn&#39;t violate content policy" vertex="1">
